Navigate through the surface of a hypersphere and kill your enemies.

* This repository has the following project as git submodule:
  https://github.com/cameron314/concurrentqueue

-> Clone with submodules using.
git clone --recursive

-> Otherwise, download submodules after cloning by running:
git submodule update --init

* Necessary packages (used in Debian 6, Ubuntu 11.04, Mint 12):
  build-essential
  cmake
  libgl1-mesa-dev
  libglew1.5-dev
  libsdl2-dev
  libboost-dev
  libopenal-dev
  libopusfile-dev

-> Debian and Ubuntu users:
sudo apt-get install build-essential cmake libgl1-mesa-dev libglu1-mesa-dev libglew1.5-dev libsdl2-dev libboost-thread-dev libboost-system-dev libguichan-0.8.1-1v5 libguichan-opengl-0.8.1-1v5 libguichan-sdl-0.8.1-1v5 libguichan-dev libopenal-dev libopusfile-dev

* Optional packages:
  Doxygen
  blender 2.59+

* Configure project:
  $ mkdir build
  $ cd build
  $ cmake ..

* Compile:
  $ make -j

* Play:
  $ cd ..
  $ build/src/sdl/glome
